---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.endsWith('/') ? import.meta.env.BASE_URL : `${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/`;
---

<BaseLayout title="Children Path | Soroban Dojo">
  <section class="path-studio-hero panel" style={`--path-mist:url('${base}graphics/worksheet-mist.svg')`}>
    <div class="path-studio-brand">
      <div class="path-studio-mark" aria-hidden="true"><img src={`${base}graphics/sakura-mark.svg`} alt="" /></div>
      <div class="content-prose">
        <p class="eyebrow">Children path · こども</p>
        <h1>Short, visual, encouraging practice</h1>
        <p>This path keeps sessions shorter, explanations warmer, and practice focused on one clear win at a time.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="path-studio-stats">
      <article class="subtle-panel path-studio-stat"><span>Best worksheet</span><strong>Foundations focus</strong></article>
      <article class="subtle-panel path-studio-stat"><span>Session length</span><strong>5–10 minutes</strong></article>
      <article class="subtle-panel path-studio-stat"><span>First win</span><strong>Read and set 31</strong></article>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a class="button" href={`${base}worksheets?preset=foundations-focus`}>Start with a worksheet</a>
      <a class="button button-secondary" href={`${base}levels/l0`}>Start at Foundations</a>
      <a class="button button-secondary" href={`${base}daily-drills`}>Use a short daily pack</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="panel content-prose">
    <p class="eyebrow">Children path</p>
    <h2>Simple order to follow</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>5–10 minute sessions</li>
      <li>More visual descriptions and reminders</li>
      <li>Gentle review instead of pressure</li>
    </ul>
    <ol>
      <li>Learn the parts of the soroban.</li>
      <li>Read and set small numbers.</li>
      <li>Add and subtract on one rod.</li>
      <li>Learn complements when direct moves get stuck.</li>
      <li>Move into bigger numbers and short worksheets.</li>
    </ol>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a class="button" href={`${base}worksheets?preset=foundations-focus`}>Start worksheet</a>
      <a class="button button-secondary" href={`${base}curriculum`}>See the full learning map</a>
      <a class="button button-secondary" href={`${base}practice`}>Try a quick exercise</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    .path-studio-hero{display:grid;gap:1rem;border:1px solid rgba(244,194,194,.55);box-shadow:0 18px 48px rgba(201,114,114,.08);background-image:linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,250,248,.95), rgba(255,244,246,.98)), var(--path-mist);background-size:cover;background-position:center bottom}
    .path-studio-brand{display:flex;gap:1rem;align-items:flex-start}.path-studio-mark{width:4.5rem;height:4.5rem;border-radius:1.5rem;background:rgba(255,255,255,.8);display:grid;place-items:center;box-shadow:0 12px 32px rgba(201,114,114,.12);flex:0 0 auto}.path-studio-mark img{width:3.25rem;height:3.25rem}.path-studio-stats{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,minmax(0,1fr));gap:.85rem}.path-studio-stat{display:grid;gap:.35rem}.path-studio-stat span{font-size:.75rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.06em;color:#9a6c6c}@media (max-width:900px){.path-studio-stats{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
  </style>

  <section class="split-grid">
    <article class="panel content-prose">
      <p class="eyebrow">First week</p>
      <h2>A gentle starter routine</h2>
      <ol>
        <li><strong>Day 1:</strong> Learn the parts of the soroban and name the beam, upper bead, and lower beads.</li>
        <li><strong>Day 2:</strong> Read small numbers like 4, 7, and 8 before moving any beads.</li>
        <li><strong>Day 3:</strong> Set two-rod numbers such as 24 and 31.</li>
        <li><strong>Day 4:</strong> Practice one-rod addition with short 5-minute rounds.</li>
        <li><strong>Day 5:</strong> Try one short worksheet or daily drill pack and stop while the energy is still good.</li>
      </ol>
      <p class="muted">A short happy finish is better than a long tired session.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="panel content-prose">
      <p class="eyebrow">First win</p>
      <h2>One simple success to aim for</h2>
      <p>By the end of the first week, a child on this path should be able to read and set a number like <strong>31</strong> calmly as a clear first win.</p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="button" href={`${base}lessons/l0/parts-of-the-soroban`}>Start first lesson</a>
        <a class="button button-secondary" href={`${base}exercises/l0/set-thirty-one`}>Try the first win</a>
      </div>
    </article>
  </section>

  <section class="panel content-prose">
    <p class="eyebrow">Best next steps</p>
    <h2>When a session goes well</h2>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a class="button" href={`${base}daily-drills`}>Generate today’s short pack</a>
      <a class="button button-secondary" href={`${base}boss-rounds`}>See milestone endings</a>
      <a class="button button-secondary" href={`${base}paths/adults`}>Compare the adult path</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
